title: #TOURNOTES: RIO RECAP
description: Between Michel's win, Kolohe's runner-up finish (and his dad's passion), skating the bowl with Bob Burnquist, and Alejo's male modeling debut, we'd say our time in Rio was well spent. Take a gander and see more from Michel and the rest of the boys at http://hurley.com/athletes.
